OL,3,CMan tried but failed to set fire to
OL,4,Cwheelie bin before pushing it at police
OL,6,FA man who tried but failed to set fire
OL,7,Fto a wheelie bin which was pushed
OL,8,Ftowards police during disorder in
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough has been jailed for 26
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FMichael Stevenson, 34, of Newport
OL,13,FRoad, Middlesbrough, was later
OL,14,Frecognised by a police officer who
OL,15,Fwatched YouTube footage of the
OL,16,Fdisorder in the town on 4 August.
