OL,3,CMan tried but failed to set fire to
OL,4,Cwheelie bin before pushing it at police
OL,6,FThe defendant could be seen trying to
OL,7,Fset fire to rubbish in a large wheelie
OL,8,Fbin which he then helped push towards
OL,9,Fpolice lines, Teesside Crown Court
OL,10,Fheard on Wednesday.
OL,12,FRachel Masters, prosecuting, said when
OL,13,Fhe was arrested four days later,
OL,14,FStevenson said he had been visited at
OL,15,Fhis home by police five years earlier
OL,16,Fand he had "acted in retaliation for
OL,17,Fthat".
OL,19,FHe admitted a single count of violent
OL,20,Fdisorder.
