OL,3,CMan tried but failed to set fire to
OL,4,Cwheelie bin before pushing it at police
OL,6,FJudge Francis Laird KC sentenced him
OL,7,Fto 26 months behind bars, saying: "You
OL,8,Fchose to take part in an organised and
OL,9,Flarge-scale act of public disorder."
OL,11,FGary Wood, defending, said Stevenson
OL,12,Fwas isolated from other people, had
OL,13,Fmental issues and will find prison
OL,14,Fvery hard.
OL,16,FAlso appearing at Teesside Crown Court
OL,17,Fwas Declan Dixon, who threw a brick at
OL,18,Fpolice during disorder in Hartlepool.
