OL,6,FHe admitted violent disorder and
OL,7,Fpossessing cocaine and Judge Francis
OL,8,FLaird KC jailed him for 18 months,
OL,9,Fsaying: "Your behaviour, and the
OL,10,Fbehaviour of others around you, was
OL,11,Fdisgraceful."
OL,13,FGary Wood, defending, said Dixon was
OL,14,Fimmature, had no previous convictions
OL,15,Fand had now lost his #1,600-a-month
OL,16,Fapprenticeship.
